    <RotR_OLHostedMood.stages.a_fleeting_haven.description>这个临时避难所给我们带来了难得的宁静和安全。但我们很快就要离开，这种感觉真是苦乐参半。</RotR_OLHostedMood.stages.a_fleeting_haven.description>
    
    <!-- EN: open arms -->
    <RotR_OLRecruitedMood.stages.open_arms.label>敞开的怀抱</RotR_OLRecruitedMood.stages.open_arms.label>
